# The simplest possible rotation: once a month, hold the three sector
# ETFs with the strongest six-month momentum. No conditions, no stops —
# dropping out of the top three IS the exit. This five-line file is a
# complete, backtestable tactical allocation strategy.

strategy "Monthly Sector Momentum"

universe [etf_sectors]
rebalance monthly

hold top 3 by [momentum 126]
